<br>
Move a bit away from the zone-in/graveyard and you can duo/group with reasonable safety.<br>
<br>
Innovation restricts your space to work in the entrance area.<br>
<br>
In Justice/Disease you need to move quite a distance away from the zone-in to hunt.<br>
